about web forms and form builder stanford answers stanford university stanford answers about web forms and form builder categories accounts and ids administrative applications anti virus and security computer operating systems connecting to the network desktop hardware and support email and calendar help desk restricted information on it services software at stanford stanford hospital and clinics telephones and cable tv unix systems and software web services user login login with your sunet id home about web forms and form builder search this site stanford faculty staff and students who have a full service sunet id and afs space can use the stanford web forms service to make contact forms short surveys and polls instructor evaluations and other forms free of charge no knowledge of html javascript or sql is required the form building application provides a selection of pre formatted fields and elements both general purpose and stanford specific as well as pre defined actions which make it quick and easy to construct web forms data collected through the forms can then be emailed to the form owner and or stored in a mysql database where it can be viewed through a secure web interface if you re new to the forms service see the getting started with the web forms service page ready to create a form or survey launch the form builder note the free qualtrics web based survey tool is also available these forms and not secure and may not be used to collect prohibited or restricted data the web forms service shares the same data security restrictions as the mysql database hosting service need help ask for help from other users on the user mailing list discuss your problem with the team working on the service submit a helpsu request web forms form builder stanford university 450 serra mall stanford california 94305 650 723 2300 terms of use copyright complaints
